                            <comment id="92200" author="hongchao.zhang" created="Fri, 22 Aug 2014 04:32:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;this should be another issue, and it was caused by the tests before these failed test (say, test_15), for the failed test failed just at the beginning,&lt;/p&gt;

